@startuml DeploymentDiagram
' PlantUML deployment diagram for Agro Data Management System
skinparam monochrome true

title Deployment: Agro Data Management System

node "Edge / Sensors" as Sensors {
  artifact "Sensor devices" as sensors_art
}

cloud "External Weather API" as WeatherAPI

node "Backend Server (Go)" as Backend {
  component "API Server" as APIServer
  component "Data Collector" as DataCollector
}

node "ML Service (Python)" as MLService {
  component "ML Model (MLP)"
}

database "Postgres DB" as Postgres

node "Message Broker" as Broker
node "Notification Service" as Notifier
node "External Notification Targets" as External

Sensors --> Backend : push metrics (HTTP/gRPC)
Backend --> WeatherAPI : request forecast (HTTP)
Backend --> MLService : send features (REST/gRPC)
MLService --> Backend : return probability P

'' High-risk alert flow (e.g., P > 0.7)
Backend --> Broker : publish alert event [P > 0.7]
Broker --> Notifier : deliver event
Notifier --> External : send email/SMS/WEBHOOK
Backend --> Postgres : write alert log

'' Normal monitoring flow (e.g., P <= 0.7)
Backend --> Postgres : write monitoring entry [P <= 0.7]

MLService --> Postgres : optional model logs

@enduml
